title: Children's Short Works Collection Vol. 016
creator: Various
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Children's Short Works Collection Vol. 016, by Various. Librivox’s Children’s Short Works Collection 016: a collection of 15 short works for children in the public domain read by a variety of Librivox members. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
